        "action": "Reform Child Maintenance \u2013 require parental mediation and proof of care",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We think child maintenance may unfairly penalise a parent. We feel the system relies on overnight stays, ignoring full parenting roles. Please reform it to require  parental mediation and proof of care before enforcement action is taken, and count all parenting time for fairness.",
